quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  31,20,"Did you not see that God brought whatever in the skies and whatever on the earth under your control (and at your service), and He abundantly gave you His favor, apparent and hidden? And some of the people argue about God without any knowledge and without any guidance and without an enlightening book"
  31,21,"And when they are told follow what God sent down, they say: no, but we follow what we found our fathers upon it. Even if Satan was inviting them to the punishment of the burning fire"
  31,22,"And anyone who submits his manner (of life) to God and he is a good doer then he has indeed grabbed on to the firm handle, and the end of the affairs is with God"
  31,23,"And anyone who disbelieves, then do not let his disbelief make you sad. Their return is to Us, and We inform them of what they did. Indeed God knows well what is inside the chests (minds)"
  31,24,"We let them enjoy for a little, then We force them to a severe punishment"
  31,25,"And if you ask them who created the skies and the earth? They shall say: God. Say: all praise belongs to God. No, but most of them do not know"
  31,26,Whatever in the skies and the earth belongs to God. Indeed God is the rich (and needless) and the praiseworthy
  31,27,"If whatever tree on the earth is (made into) pens, and the sea fill it up (with ink) and seven more seas (replenish it) after that, God’s words would not finish. Indeed God is powerful and knowledgeable"
  31,28,Your creation and your resurrection is only like (creation of) a single person. Indeed God hears all and sees all
  31,29,"Did you not see that God makes the night pass through the day and makes the day pass through the night, and He controlled the sun and the moon, each running (its course) in a finite time, and God is well informed of what you do"
  31,30,"That is because God is the truth, and that whatever they call on other than Him is the falsehood, and that God is the superior, the great"
  31,31,"Or did you not see that the ship sails in the sea by God’s favor, so that He shows you some of His signs? For there are certainly signs in that for every patient and thankful (person)"
  31,32,"And when a wave covers them like the shades, they call on God being sincere to Him in the religion, then when He saves them to the land, some of them keep to the middle course, and no one rejects Our signs except every ungrateful traitor"
  31,33,"People, be cautious of your Master and fear a day when no father repays for his child and no child can repay anything for his father. Indeed God’s promise is true, so do not be deceived by this world’s life, and do not be deceived by the deceiver (Satan) about God"
  31,34,"Indeed knowledge of the hour is with God, and He sends down the rain and knows what is in the wombs, and no one knows what it will do tomorrow and no one knows in which land it will die. Indeed God is knowledgeable and well informed"